Package be.ac.ulb.infof307.g09.application.controllers.user

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HomeController
    Home Controller class that handles actions in the Home UI, such as adding or deletion of tabs.
    LoginController
    Login controller class handles the login view with a register or a connection option of a user.
    ProfileController
    The profile controller class handle all the data of the user's profile (username, firstname, lastname, email, password).
    RegisterController
    Register controller handles the register scene with all the fields that the new user has to field his new profile data.
